snippet.title: Paragraph 78 (2007) - Full Gameplay Walkthrough / (PC)
snippet.description:
Thank you MasterromaN for the translation
All scenes from movie cutted. Full Gameplay Walkthrough of the game Paragraph 78 (2007).
In the near future, a crew of Special Forces` ex-members is assigned to an important mission--a unique opportunity for long-retired commandos to reconnect with their brothers in arms.
